# The username of an ESP32 is its exact GerNetiX device_id. A registered
# device can receive only its own OTA notification and publish only its own
# operational status or project telemetry. The internal Build-&-Deploy and
# Telemetry connections use the isolated
# non-TLS listener and is not evaluated against this external-device ACL.
pattern read gernetix/devices/%u/ota
pattern read gernetix/devices/%u/flashbox/jobs
pattern write gernetix/devices/%u/status/#
pattern write gernetix/devices/%u/telemetry
